    287          /*********************************************************************
    288           * @fn      Batt_GetParameter
    289           *
    290           * @brief   Get a Battery Service parameter.
    291           *
    292           * @param   param - Profile parameter ID
    293           * @param   value - pointer to data to get.  This is dependent on
